data.text:
Invest in San Diego Families (ISDF) is a coalition fighting for a San Diego County that is for the people and by the people. We fight for an economy, and government that puts power into the hands of regular people.

– Alliance of Californians for Community Empowerment (ACCE) Action

– ACLU of San Diego and Imperial Counties
